Package com.hazelcast.config

Class JoinConfig

java.lang.Object
com.hazelcast.config.JoinConfig
public class JoinConfig
extends Object
Contains the 3 different join configurations; TCP-IP/multicast/AWS. Only one of them should be enabled!
